OL,3,CWater firm boss repeatedly refuses to
OL,4,Csay if she will give up bonus
OL,6,FNicola Shaw is asked three times about
OL,7,Fwhat 'sacrifices' she is prepared to
OL,8,Fmake on the day Yorkshire Water said
OL,9,Fbills would rise 41%
OL,11,FThe boss of Yorkshire Water has
OL,12,Frepeatedly refused to say whether she
OL,13,Fwould give up her bonus after the
OL,14,Fcompany announced that customers'
OL,15,Fbills will increase by 41% in the next
OL,16,Ffive years.
