OL,3,CWater firm boss repeatedly refuses to
OL,4,Csay if she will give up bonus
OL,6,FHouseholders' average annual bills
OL,7,Fwill go up #177 from #430 this year to
OL,8,F#607 by 2029 to fund what the company
OL,9,Fsays are essential improvements to the
OL,10,Fwater network.
OL,12,FIt comes as the regulator Ofwat
OL,13,Fannounced that customers across the
OL,14,Fcountry are facing price rises to pay
OL,15,Ffor a #104 billion upgrade of the
OL,16,Fsystem nationally.
OL,18,FBut there has been anger from consumer
OL,19,Fgroups at the charges in the wake of
OL,20,Flarge bonus payouts and record levels
OL,21,Fof pollution.
