OL,3,CWater firm boss repeatedly refuses to
OL,4,Csay if she will give up bonus
OL,6,FYorkshire Water's chief executive
OL,7,FNicola Shaw received a #371,000 bonus
OL,8,Fin 2023-24 , along with a salary and
OL,9,Fpension package worth #657,000.
OL,11,FWhen asked directly by ITV Calendar
OL,12,FNews whether she would give up her
OL,13,Fbonus in light of the bill rise, Ms
OL,14,FShaw avoided the question.
OL,16,FShe said: "The business, as we've said
OL,17,Ffor some time, is a turnaround.
OL,18,FThere's a lot more to do and we're
OL,19,Fworking really hard to keep improving.
