OL,3,CWater firm boss repeatedly refuses to
OL,4,Csay if she will give up bonus
OL,6,FAsked a third time if she and others
OL,7,Fwho receive dividends would be
OL,8,Fprepared to make sacrifices, she said:
OL,9,F"Our shareholders have already
OL,10,Fcommitted to putting in another
OL,11,F#500million in at least before the end
OL,12,Fof March 2027 so this is a joint
OL,13,Feffort by them."
OL,15,FThe average bill nationally will go up
OL,16,Fby #31 a year over the next five
OL,17,Fyears, Ofwat said - significantly more
OL,18,Fthan the expected increase of around
OL,19,F#20 a year per household, outlined in
OL,20,Fthe regulator's draft proposals in
OL,21,FJuly.
